extends layout

block content
  h1 API help

  p Access the api by calling 
    span.code /api
  p The api allows to access, add, remove and update 
  | users, projects and frames.
  | What you are really looking for is frames, 
  | they contain the segments.

  p
  |  this is a restful api, access to 
  span.code /api/u
  |  for users, 
  span.code /api/p
  |  for projects and 
  span.code /api/f
  |  for frames.

  p For further info, please contact 
    each a in admins
      span= a.name +': '
      a(href='mailto:'+a.email)= a.email

  hr
  section
    form(action='/api/p', method='post')#f
      label new project
        input(name='title')#title
        button(type='submit') create
    span#result